+ Class Methods

++ Public

* Solar_App_Hello::__construct() -- Constructor.

* Solar_App_Hello::__get() -- Try to force users to define what their view variables are.

* Solar_App_Hello::__set() -- Try to force users to define what their view variables are.

* Solar_App_Hello::addFlash() -- Appends a "read-once" session value for this class and key.

* Solar_App_Hello::apiVersion() -- Reports the API version for this class.

* Solar_App_Hello::display() -- Executes the requested action and displays its output.

* Solar_App_Hello::fetch() -- Executes the requested action and returns its output with layout.

* Solar_App_Hello::getFlash() -- Retrieves a "read-once" session value, thereby removing the value.

* Solar_App_Hello::locale() -- Looks up locale strings based on a key.

* Solar_App_Hello::setFlash() -- Sets a "read-once" session value for this class and a key.

++ Protected

* Solar_App_Hello::_actionFile() -- Returns the file name for an action.

* Solar_App_Hello::_collect() -- Collects action, pathinfo, and query values.

* Solar_App_Hello::_exception() -- Convenience method for returning exceptions with localized text.

* Solar_App_Hello::_forward() -- Forwards to an action script.

* Solar_App_Hello::_info() -- Retrieve the TAINTED value of a pathinfo request key by name.

* Solar_App_Hello::_postAction() -- Executes just after the last action, and just before the view.

* Solar_App_Hello::_preAction() -- Executes just before the first action.

* Solar_App_Hello::_query() -- Retrieves the TAINTED value of a query request key by name.

* Solar_App_Hello::_redirect() -- Redirects to another URL.

* Solar_App_Hello::_run() -- Includes a file in an isolated scope (but with access to $this).

* Solar_App_Hello::_setup() -- Hook for extended setup behaviors.

++ Private

None.